message: Miguel S. Arnold, 32, convicted in federal court for his role in a sex trafficking operation that exploited over 20 victims, including juveniles.

data.description: HARRISBURG, Pa. (WHTM) – A Harrisburg man has been convicted in federal court for his role in a sex trafficking operation that exploited over 20 victims, including juveniles, authorities said…
data.title: Harrisburg man convicted of sex trafficking
